WEBVTT

00:08:00.394 --> 00:08:02.982
Na ninapomaliza hii hotuba yangu,

00:08:03.006 --> 00:08:06.254
Ninapendelea kuuliza kila mmoja wenu hapa,

00:08:07.744 --> 00:08:11.625
wasomi wakuu, waleta mabadiliko, wavumbuzi,

00:08:11.649 --> 00:08:14.752
watu wote kutoka ulimwenguni mliopo hapa TED,

00:08:14.776 --> 00:08:17.259
kumbuka maneno ya Martin Luther King.

00:08:17.958 --> 00:08:20.545
Yaache yaendelee kusikika katika moyo na maisha yako.

00:08:21.252 --> 00:08:23.035
Vyovyote ilivyo,

00:08:23.059 --> 00:08:24.685
popote ulipo,

00:08:24.709 --> 00:08:26.392
chochote inachogharimu,

00:08:26.416 --> 00:08:27.567
endelea mbele.

00:08:27.591 --> 00:08:28.750
Asante.

00:08:28.774 --> 00:08:32.151
(Makofi)